Title: Carteles de Cine
Summary: Over 1300 posters from 1960s-2016 designed by Cuban artists for both Cuban and foreign films, film festivals, and film related special events. Posters were commissioned by Cinemateca de Cuba, part of Instituto Cubano del Arte e Industria Cinematográficos.
Contents note: Digitized as part of the International Digital Ephemera Project (IDEP); publication dates of contents range from approximately 1960 to 2016.
Repository: Cinemateca de Cuba, Instituto Cubano del Arte e Industria Cinematográficos
Subject topic: Motion pictures -- Cuba -- Posters|~|Graphic arts -- Cuba
